  Item(name: 'Jupiter', image: 'Jupiter', avatar: 'Jupiter',
      description: "Jupiter is the fifth planet from the Sun and the largest in the Solar System. A gas giant, "
          "Jupiter's mass is more than two and a half times that of all the other planets in the Solar System combined "
